strings: <se_def>*: If you're traveling to the land of snow, stay here to stay warm.
<se_def>*: From there, head northwest and enter a large snowy area through a cave.
<se_def>*: I want to see snow with my own eyes, but it's too cold. My teeth ache just thinking about it!
<se_def>*: I live in a church and hope that one day I will gather the courage to go.
